 @endspecial 1057 2012 a(A)p BrickRed 20 w Ff(star)q(t)p
Black 19 w Fi(vertex.)27 b(Her)o(e)19 b Fh(u)g Fi(is)h(ascending,)g
Fh(v)j Fi(descending,)c(and)h Fh(v)3025 2004 y Fd(\017)3072
