 @endspecial 1057 2604 a(An)p BrickRed 20 w Ff(end)p
Black 18 w Fi(vertex.)k(Her)o(e)19 b Fh(u)g Fi(is)h(descending,)g
Fh(v)j Fi(ascending,)d(and)g Fh(v)3040 2596 y Fd(\017)3088
2604 y Fh(u)3136 2574 y Fd(?)3214 2604 y Fh(>)j Fe(0)p
Fi(.)142 3444 y @beginspecial 0 @llx 0 @lly 84 @urx 64
